title: How has the proportion of obese 4-5 year old children changed over time?
analysis_commentary: The proportion of reception aged children who are overweight or obese was approximately 22% in 2014/15. Overall, the percent of reception aged children who are overweight, obese or underweight has remained broadly stable between 2006/07 and 2014/15.
